  "texts": [
    "Only a few people knew the truth and they were forbidden from being honest about it for reasons of national security.",
    "It has been many decades and no other country has been able to land on the moon, even though countries like China absolutely would have the funds and motivation to do so in order to showcase their own technology to the world.",
    "This cluster of statements centers on the conspiracy theory that the Apollo moon landings were fabricated.",
    "These assertions highlight skepticism about the authenticity of the moon landing, suggesting that it was staged by the US government or NASA to win the space race against the Soviet Union, enhance national prestige, or for other geopolitical or propaganda reasons.",
